name: Sacred Prayer Among Digital Layer
description:
This is real life. We’re not living with the old methods that use contemporary paradigms anymore, but now also adapting to the formulas, logic and algorithms. Yes, that's life, it’ll be so complicated when we described by words. Everyone has their own perspective and resolution. Everyone has their own stage and spotlight. But what we always hold on to in living this life is that we always do something good, and we pray for each other to make our lives better.

————————
